The evidence with the title 'WhatsApp: how the supermarket voucher scam works - BBC News ' says Nov 7, 2017  ... Scammers are using WhatsApp to send fake supermarket vouchers to trick people into revealing their details  ... A screenshot from WhatsApp showing the scam which reads ALDI is giving away £ 150 Free  ... Message to 20 other contacts in order to receive a £ 250 voucher .  ... Brexit : what could happen next? 
